<emphasis id="56968456FFEC6825FEBDCCC78CD0EB62" bold="true" box="[264,408,1785,1809]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">FIGURE 23.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="A3E223C7FFEC6825FE1DCCC48F86EB62" authority="(Flint)" authorityName="Blahnik Table Of Contents" authorityYear="2005" baseAuthorityName="Blahnik Table Of Contents" baseAuthorityYear="2005" box="[424,718,1786,1809]" class="Insecta" family="Philopotamidae" genus="Alterosa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanctipauli">
<emphasis id="56968456FFEC6825FE1DCCC48F37EB62" box="[424,639,1786,1809]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Alterosa sanctipauli</emphasis>
(Flint)
</taxonomicName>
. Male genitalia: 23A—lateral view; 23B—dorsal view of segments IX and X; 23C—inferior appendage, dorsal view; 23D—phallic apparatus, lateral view.
</paragraph>
</caption>
